      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample size adequate for statistical characterization of construct stiffness and failure load variability."
