      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single load condition (ASTM F1717 standard compression-bending configuration). Absence of additional load cases (e.g., torsion, fatigue) limits coverage of the full mechanical environment. Achieved level 1 does not meet required level 2; this gap is documented as an accepted limitation by the credibility assessment team."
