      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry and loading head displacement rate. Preload torque applied to set screw modeled via equivalent pretension elements calibrated to measured clamp force."
