    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test conditions factor achieving level 1 against a required level 2. The assessment team determined that the single ASTM F1717 load case is sufficient for the stated regulatory claim and that the shortfall is bounded by the conservative nature of the standard test protocol. All remaining 12 factors meet or exceed required levels.",
